urls.title: Taiwan releases December email to WHO showing unheeded warning about coronavirus
urls.description: The World Health Organization (WHO) is under fire after Taiwan released the contents of a December email inquiring about the person to person spread of COVID-19, saying it was instead ignored by WHO and denied adequate information to fight the virus.
